<%- include('../partials/header', { title: 'User Guide - Missing Person Report System' }) %>

<main class="guide-content">
  <div class="guide-container">
    <a href="/" class="back-btn">&larr; Back to Home</a>
    <div class="guide-header">
      <h1>User Guide</h1>
      <p class="guide-subtitle">Learn how to use the Missing Person Report System effectively</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guide-navigation">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#introduction">Introduction</a></li>
        <li><a href="#user-roles">User Roles</a></li>
        <li><a href="#reporting-missing">Reporting a Missing Person</a></li>
        <li><a href="#reporting-found">Reporting a Found Person</a></li>
        <li><a href="#dashboard">Using Your Dashboard</a></li>
        <li><a href="#faq">Frequently Asked Questions</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <section id="introduction" class="guide-section">
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>The Missing Person Report System is designed to help reunite missing persons with their families. Our platform connects those who have lost someone with those who may have found them, creating a bridge between families and the community.</p>
      
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="info-content">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>To provide a secure, efficient platform that helps reunite missing persons with their families through community collaboration and real-time information sharing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="user-roles" class="guide-section">
      <h2>User Roles</h2>
      <p>The system has three main user roles, each with specific capabilities:</p>
      
      <div class="role-cards">
        <div class="role-card">
          <div class="role-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
              <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Public Users</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Browse missing and found person cases</li>
            <li>Report found persons</li>
            <li>View the case status</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="role-card">
          <div class="role-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
              <path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5C14.34 5 13 6.34 13 8s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Registered Users</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>All public user capabilities</li>
            <li>Report missing persons</li>
            <li>Access personal dashboard</li>
            <li>Receive case updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="role-card">
          <div class="role-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
              <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Administrators</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>All registered user capabilities</li>
            <li>Manage all cases</li>
            <li>Update case status</li>
            <li>Verify reports</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="reporting-missing" class="guide-section">
      <h2>Reporting a Missing Person</h2>
      <p>If someone you know is missing, follow these steps to report it:</p>
      
      <div class="step-cards">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Register or Login</h3>
          <p>Create an account or log in to your existing account to access dash-board features</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Access the Dashboard</h3>
          <p>From your dashboard, select "Parent Report Cases" to view existing report.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>Fill the Report Form</h3>
          <p>Provide accurate information including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Missing person's name, age, and gender</li>
            <li>Last seen location and date</li>
            <li>Recent photo (if available)</li>
            <li>Description of clothing and appearance</li>
            <li>Your contact information</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
      </div>
      
    </section>

    <section id="reporting-found" class="guide-section">
      <h2>Reporting a Found Person</h2>
      <p>If you've found someone who appears to be missing or in need of help, you can report it through our  with the help of any police.:</p>
      
      <div class="step-cards">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Access the Report Form</h3>
          <p>You don't need to be registered to report a found person find any police and submit the report.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Provide Details</h3>
          <p>Include as much information as possible:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Approximate age and gender</li>
            <li>Location where the person was found</li>
            <li>Date and time</li>
            <li>Description of appearance and condition</li>
            <li>Your contact information</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
      
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="info-content">
          <h3>Safety First</h3>
          <p>If the person appears to be in immediate danger or requires medical attention, contact emergency services (911).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="browsing-cases" class="guide-section">
      <h2>Browsing Cases</h2>
      <p>You can see both missing and found person cases to help identify potential matches:</p>
      
      <div class="feature-cards">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Missing Person Cases</h3>
          <p>View active cases of reported missing persons. Each case includes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Photo and basic information</li>
            <li>Last seen location and date</li>
            <li>Case status</li>
      
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Found Person Cases</h3>
          <p>Review reports of found persons to help identify them:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Approximate age and gender</li>
            <li>Location where found</li>
            <li>Date found</li>
            <li>Description and condition</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="dashboard" class="guide-section">
      <h2>Using Your Dashboard</h2>
      <p>Registered users have access to the dashboard with the following features:</p>
      
      <div class="dashboard-features">
        <div class="dashboard-feature">
          <h3>Case view</h3>
          <p>View your reported cases, including checking status.</p>
        </div>
        
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="info-content">
          <h3>Accessing Your Dashboard</h3>
          <p>Log in to your account and you'll be automatically directed to your dashboard. From there, you can navigate to all available features.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" class="guide-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="faq-container">

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I update the report?</h3>
          <p>No, registered users can not update the reports as admin(Police) is the repoter from your side</p>
        </div>

        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is my information kept confidential?</h3>
          <p>Yes, we take privacy seriously. Your personal contact information is only shared with administrators.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I volunteer to help with searches?</h3>
          <p>Yes! Registered users can indicate their willingness to volunteer. When a case is reported in your area, you may be notified of opportunities to assist.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="guide-footer">
      <h2>Need Additional Help?</h2>
      <p>If you have questions not covered in this guide, please contact our support team:</p>
      <a href="mailto:support@missingpersonfinder.com" class="support-link">support@missingpersonfinder.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

